<HEADLINE>
FT  07 AUG 93 / Finance and the Family: Smaller companies rise - At a glance
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
ANOTHER good week for smaller company shares with the Hoare Govett Smaller
Companies index (capital gains version) rising 2.2 per cent over the seven
days to August 5, from 1478.91 to 1511.33.
</TEXT>
<XX>
